text.tspan: Israel: New hospitalizations for COVID-19 by age
Shown is the rolling weekly sum of COVID-19 hospitalizations. Data is available at the national level, plus breakdown
by regions where vaccination began early or late.
Vaccination in Israel began on December 19 2020. Israel imposed a third national lockdown on January 8 2021.
